bah...all of these replies are for bloob servers...so my advice might be limited.  on pvp server, you cant charm other players pets, period.  with respect to cerilius' post...sure, you can pumice a dot, but how many pumices is a person willing to blow through before they decide its cheaper to die?  sure, someone who has been on the server a long time might have ubermega pp to burn on carrying 30 pumice stones everywhere he goes, but most players dont.

with respect to the post saying the chanter can cast a pet, speed and mr buff it...sure you can, just ask the necro to have a smoke and coffee while you get ready...

i guess all of you are speaking from the bloob servers perspective, so your points are valid, but on red servers, there is no "lemme get a pet" time.

dueling and pvping are two different things.

to beat a chanter (of any level) lich + lt dots + mr = dead chanter.  he will run out of mana before you do.

The best thing to do when trying to trouble shoot pc issues is to try and remember the last thing you did before it started acting strangely, then empty a clip from a .45 cal pistol into the case...followed by tequilla shots.
